##..: Separation line
##
${color3}${alignc}${cpubar cpu6 0, 200}
${color2}${voffset 5}${font Nimbus Mono L:size=9 style=bold}${alignc}SCHOOL
${color3}${font Nimbus Mono S:size=5 style=bold}${execi 500 cat $HOME/.todo/todo.school}
${color3}${alignc}${cpubar cpu6 0, 200}
